  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818480/extras/f44d9387a4c3e913111b0bef7643bdfb.avif?t=1738685598\" width=612 height=114 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818480/extras/1925e3dfa21d045a6ed9d9aae9d9a232.webp?t=1738685598\" width=600 height=52 /></span>You are the owner of a delivery point in a small district.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Give out parcels</strong> to the coming people or <strong>deliver</strong> them to their doors. The only rule - be fast, nobody likes to wait.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade yourself and your delivery point to be effective, hire people to work for you or play with friends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818480/extras/b41b68d5ce1c2c25df903ac339596ef3.poster.avif?t=1738685598\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818480/extras/b41b68d5ce1c2c25df903ac339596ef3.webm?t=1738685598\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818480/extras/b41b68d5ce1c2c25df903ac339596ef3.mp4?t=1738685598\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818480/extras/576c5b18259e3cbe8205640c3ad4fc72.webp?t=1738685598\" width=600 height=52 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Door-to-door delivery</strong> - take the parcel and get it to its destination. There awaits lots of <strong>obstacles</strong> in your way so be careful, you can easily <strong>trip and damage</strong> the package</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818480/extras/0948f334106e93a8fae8c2e3a4cfb972.poster.avif?t=1738685598\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818480/extras/0948f334106e93a8fae8c2e3a4cfb972.webm?t=1738685598\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818480/extras/0948f334106e93a8fae8c2e3a4cfb972.mp4?t=1738685598\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are free to choose your own way of delivery - drink energy drinks and run as fast as you can or try to find the shortcuts in <strong>sandboxes</strong> and <strong>garbage chutes!</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818480/extras/7fb5c02e018707022cf01607314777f9.poster.avif?t=1738685598\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818480/extras/7fb5c02e018707022cf01607314777f9.webm?t=1738685598\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818480/extras/7fb5c02e018707022cf01607314777f9.mp4?t=1738685598\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play <strong>solo</strong> or make <strong>a group of 4</strong> with your friends, so you can be the most efficient delivery point in district! But keep them in check - they can <strong>sabotage</strong> your work!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818480/extras/7bdf1a407792eb84e7d3a2d2b0472bc5.poster.avif?t=1738685598\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818480/extras/7bdf1a407792eb84e7d3a2d2b0472bc5.webm?t=1738685598\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818480/extras/7bdf1a407792eb84e7d3a2d2b0472bc5.mp4?t=1738685598\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try not to do <strong>anything illegal</strong> or lawman will catch you and put you to <strong>jail</strong> (there is nothing to do, honestly)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818480/extras/56bbc03fb0e79c3ec2dd4f9696c0a7b9.poster.avif?t=1738685598\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818480/extras/56bbc03fb0e79c3ec2dd4f9696c0a7b9.webm?t=1738685598\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818480/extras/56bbc03fb0e79c3ec2dd4f9696c0a7b9.mp4?t=1738685598\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Earn money</strong>, buy short-time <strong>power-ups</strong> or save up for  more valuable <strong>upgrades</strong> in the shop that will less your struggles! (Or buy your teammate out from the jail)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take care of yourself - <strong>watch out for the dirt</strong> so you won't damage customers' orders</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818480/extras/f44d9387a4c3e913111b0bef7643bdfb.avif?t=1738685598\" width=612 height=114 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818480/extras/1925e3dfa21d045a6ed9d9aae9d9a232.webp?t=1738685598\" width=600 height=52 /></span>You are the owner of a delivery point in a small district.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Give out parcels</strong> to the coming people or <strong>deliver</strong> them to their doors. The only rule - be fast, nobody likes to wait.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade yourself and your delivery point to be effective, hire people to work for you or play with friends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818480/extras/b41b68d5ce1c2c25df903ac339596ef3.poster.avif?t=1738685598\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818480/extras/b41b68d5ce1c2c25df903ac339596ef3.webm?t=1738685598\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818480/extras/b41b68d5ce1c2c25df903ac339596ef3.mp4?t=1738685598\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818480/extras/576c5b18259e3cbe8205640c3ad4fc72.webp?t=1738685598\" width=600 height=52 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Door-to-door delivery</strong> - take the parcel and get it to its destination. There awaits lots of <strong>obstacles</strong> in your way so be careful, you can easily <strong>trip and damage</strong> the package</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818480/extras/0948f334106e93a8fae8c2e3a4cfb972.poster.avif?t=1738685598\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818480/extras/0948f334106e93a8fae8c2e3a4cfb972.webm?t=1738685598\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818480/extras/0948f334106e93a8fae8c2e3a4cfb972.mp4?t=1738685598\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are free to choose your own way of delivery - drink energy drinks and run as fast as you can or try to find the shortcuts in <strong>sandboxes</strong> and <strong>garbage chutes!</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818480/extras/7fb5c02e018707022cf01607314777f9.poster.avif?t=1738685598\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818480/extras/7fb5c02e018707022cf01607314777f9.webm?t=1738685598\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818480/extras/7fb5c02e018707022cf01607314777f9.mp4?t=1738685598\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play <strong>solo</strong> or make <strong>a group of 4</strong> with your friends, so you can be the most efficient delivery point in district! But keep them in check - they can <strong>sabotage</strong> your work!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818480/extras/7bdf1a407792eb84e7d3a2d2b0472bc5.poster.avif?t=1738685598\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818480/extras/7bdf1a407792eb84e7d3a2d2b0472bc5.webm?t=1738685598\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818480/extras/7bdf1a407792eb84e7d3a2d2b0472bc5.mp4?t=1738685598\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try not to do <strong>anything illegal</strong> or lawman will catch you and put you to <strong>jail</strong> (there is nothing to do, honestly)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818480/extras/56bbc03fb0e79c3ec2dd4f9696c0a7b9.poster.avif?t=1738685598\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818480/extras/56bbc03fb0e79c3ec2dd4f9696c0a7b9.webm?t=1738685598\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818480/extras/56bbc03fb0e79c3ec2dd4f9696c0a7b9.mp4?t=1738685598\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Earn money</strong>, buy short-time <strong>power-ups</strong> or save up for  more valuable <strong>upgrades</strong> in the shop that will less your struggles! (Or buy your teammate out from the jail)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take care of yourself - <strong>watch out for the dirt</strong> so you won't damage customers' orders</p></li></ul>",
